{"title":"光荣行——庆祝中国共产党成立八十周年","authors":["张藩"],"dates":[{"year":2001,"month":6,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣行"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——庆祝中国共产党成立八十周年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张藩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八十历程铸辉煌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"穿越风雨历沧桑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为何天地铺锦绣？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为何山河尽春光？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党旗指路光荣行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"峥嵘岁月汇交响。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长夜难明灾难重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豺狼当道民遭殃。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南湖红船播火种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一桨划破千重浪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马列真理传天下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唤醒神州向太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋收起义烈火燃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"投身革命举刀枪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三湾改编指方向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浴血罗霄战旗扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星星火苗能燎原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱散黑暗见曙光。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁流二万五千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"突破重围不可挡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌后三年游击战，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出生入死本领强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赤胆忠心跟党走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长矛大刀打胜仗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八年抗战泣鬼神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"击败强盗救危亡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三载决战惊天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"百万雄师渡大江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"痛歼蒋匪迎解放，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜看红日出东方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开国大典铸丰碑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扬眉吐气喜洋洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少英雄抛头颅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"功昭日月美名扬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少先烈洒热血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染红江山幸福长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三中全会响春雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华阔步奔富强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改革潮涌万山绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开放风吹百花香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨龙腾飞新世纪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"继往开来向前方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"回首我党八十载，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为民造福昭人心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宗承发展马列毛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民才是真英雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掌舵远航兴华夏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长征接力有人传。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"九"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"少小铁心追求党，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"戎马征途不迷航。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高举旗帜斗志坚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"维护核心豪情壮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银发赤心雄风在，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"光荣归功伟大党！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者1955年被授予中将军衔，现年九十四岁。）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}